# ðŸ§ª Storybook & CI Quality Standards

- Stories should exemplify component usage with various states (default, disabled, interactive).
- Use `@storybook/addon-a11y`, `addon-docs`, `addon-vitest`, `addon-onboarding`.
- Use **Vitest** or **Jest** in Storybook for component-level tests.
- Run `eslint .` on all `.tsx`, `.ts`, `.js`, `.jsx` files; follow existing ESLint config.
- Clean up unused imports/variables; fix lint warnings automatically.
- Ensure story snapshots and accessibility checks are included in CI.
